<TextSection>
  <h3 id="cant-hurt-me">1. "Can't Hurt Me" by David Goggins</h3>
  <p>
    David Goggins, a retired Navy SEAL, motivator, and endurance athlete, is
    known for his remarkable athletic achievements and perseverance.
  </p>
  <p>
    In his book 'Can't Hurt Me,' David details his life and career struggles,
    including his upbringing, his time in the military, and getting into
    ultra-distance running.
  </p>
  <p>
    He also takes you through his fitness challenges and how he managed to break
    records. He also offers valuable insights into overcoming personal
    challenges by developing mental and physical strength.
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
