<TextSection mxw="">
  <h3 id="the-last-dance">
    3. Michael Jordan: “The Last Dance” by Michael Leahy
  </h3>
  <p>
    Basketball legend Michael Jordan's “The Last Dance” is a memoir that talks
    about the most important game of his career, which took place on Father's
    Day, 1996.
  </p>
  <p>
    It captures the events leading up to the game, where he almost broke down in
    tears, the game itself, and the aftermath. The book also offers insights
    into the mindset of the greatest basketball player of all time.
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
