  <h3 id="serena">4. "Open" by Andre Agassi</h3>
  <p>
    Serena Williams, one of the most acclaimed sports personalities, recommended
    “Open” by Andre Agassi as one of the best sports books of all time.
  </p>
  <p>
    The book talks about Andre Agassi's journey as a tennis player and his rise
    to fame. It also shares his struggles with personal issues and how he dealt
    with them.
  </p>
