    5. "The Miracle of Castel Di Sangro" by Joe McGinniss
  </h3>
  <p>
    The renowned football manager Jose Mourinho recommends “The Miracle of
    Castel Di Sangro” by Joe McGinniss as a must-read book for sports lovers.
  </p>
  <p>
    The book talks about the triumphs and struggles of a small-town Italian
    football team, Castel Di Sangro, as they progress to the top tier of Italian
    football.
  </p>
